FBIS4-64981 "drweu091_h_94004" FBIS-WEU-94-091 Daily Report 10 May 1994 GERMANY Asylum Denied for Kurds With Turkey Safe Haven Asylum Denied for Kurds With Turkey Safe Haven LD1005194694 Berlin N-TV in German 1900 GMT 10 May 94 LD1005194694 Berlin N-TV German BFN [Excerpt] Torture in Turkey does not constitute adequate grounds for granting Kurds asylum. Under a verdict by the Federal Administrative Court in Berlin, Kurds in the Federal Republic can only claim asylum if they have no safe haven in Turkey. The court thus turned down an application for asylum by a Kurdish family from southeastern Turkey. [passage omitted]
